      "span_text": "Neurogenin-related 1 (Ngnr1), the first proneural factor of the cascade, induces the activation of lateracting basic helix-loop-helix (bHLH)  factor neuronal differentiation 1 (NeuroD); this activation ultimately defines three prospective patches of primary neurons marked by the expression of N-tubulin in the neural plate in Xenopus (10 -13) ."
